# 🌌 Galaxy Expense Tracker

A modern Expense Tracker built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** with a beautiful Galaxy-themed UI.

## ✨ Features

- 💰 Set Monthly Budget
- ➕ Add Expenses
- ✏️ Edit Expenses
- ❌ Delete Expenses
- 💾 Save Data using Local Storage
- 📊 Expense Summary by Category
- 🥧 Interactive Pie Chart
- 💵 Remaining Budget Calculation
- 🌌 Galaxy Inspired Responsive UI

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Chart.js
- Local Storage API

